Introduction

LUN8 is an eight-member boy group under Fantagio. They made their official debut on June 15, 2023, with the mini album "Continue?".

The name of the fandom, "LUV8" represents fans "who love all eight members of LUN8". By combining the verb "love" with the suffix "-ate", it becomes an adjective similar to "lovely" and "loving", which describes the member's feelings about the fans.

On January 20, 2025 Fantagio announced that members Dohyun and Eunho would be going on hiatus due to health issues while also announcing the departure of Eunseop due to health reasons.

On Febuary 6th, 2025 Fantagio announced that Yuma (a former Fantasy Boys contestant) would be officially joining the group in April.
